Key Match Events: Netherlands won by 6 wickets (with 8 balls remaining)
Pre-Game Insights: Netherlands may have been here and done it before, while Nepal have only featured in one previous T20 World Cup
Dipendra Singh Airee, the man who can change - and finish off - a T20 game singlehandedly
